\"place\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known as The SpecialOlympics, the event was founded on this day in 1968 by Eunice Kennedy Shriver - sister of formerUSpresident John F Kennedy - to provide sporting competition and training for people with intellectual disabilities (IDs), which affect cognitive and adaptive function, such as learning, problem solving and communication skills.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eunice_Kennedy_Shriver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eunice Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eunice_Kennedy_Shriver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eunice_Kennedy_Shriver\"}, {\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.993891044397278e-54, \"text\": \"John F Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The SpecialOlympics\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting competition\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"intellectual disabilities\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"IDs\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"cognitive and adaptive function\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"learning\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"problem\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"skills\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Participants might have Down Syndrome, Fetal Alcohol Syndrome, or Fragile X syndrome - but these games are all about championing what they can do, rather than what they might not be able to.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Participants\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"Down Syndrome\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"Fetal Alcohol Syndrome\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"Fragile X syndrome\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"these games\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Start your day informed with Metro'sNews Updatesnewsletter or getBreaking Newsalerts the moment it happens.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your day\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro'sNews Updatesnewsletter\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"getBreaking Newsalerts\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Special Olympics made its way across the pond a decade later, with the GB charity growing from a single swimming club for people with IDs to a network of 95 programmes across England, Scotland and Wales.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999721148137624, \"rank\": 2.788596361007268e-05, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999516148628451, \"rank\": 4.473745500242897e-05, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\