20, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like the Olympics, the Special Olympics hold summer and winter World Games every four years.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"the Special Olympics\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1689}, {\"ngram\": \"summer\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"winter World Games\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So while huge global audiences will be watching the incredible achievements of our Olympic and Paralympic athletes in Paris - with good reason - Metro is shining a light on this lesser known but vitally important event.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.787947493943082e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"huge global audiences\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"the incredible achievements\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"our Olympic and Paralympic athletes\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"good reason\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"a light\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1913}, {\"ngram\": \"this lesser known but vitally important event\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eunice Kennedy Shriver believed that the Olympic ideals of sportsmanship could give hope and confidence to people with IDs - and those values are still at the core of Team GB's plans decades later.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eunice_Kennedy_Shriver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eunice Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eunice_Kennedy_Shriver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eunice_Kennedy_Shriver\"}, {\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999969226903032, \"rank\": 2.924969752459763e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic ideals\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"sportsmanship\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"IDs\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"those values\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"the core\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Baxter, Special Olympics GB's current chief executive, had never heard of the charity until she was asked to host a football session for people with IDs nearly 20 years ago.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2164, \"end\": 2169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999793912988887, \"rank\": 2.060912583645179e-05, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baxter_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.790908162326029e-15, \"text\": \"Baxter\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baxter_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baxter_International\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Special Olympics GB's current chief executive\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"the charity\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"a football session\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"IDs\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I'd never worked with anybody with a disability before, and almost had a fear of working with anyone who wasn't from the mainstream,' she tells Metro 'But that session gave me the bug.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"a disability\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"a fear\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"the mainstream\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"that session\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"the bug\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You see an instant difference when teaching new football skills, that's one thing, but coming away from that initial session you could see that you were doing something a lot more.\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an instant difference\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"new football skills\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"that initial session\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You were teaching confidence, you were providing the opportunity for people to connect with others, you were providing a safe space for people who have to battle every day.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2790}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"a safe space\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When you start to build that out, running one sport session then contributes to that wider social impact.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one sport session\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"that wider social impact\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It developed from that one session to a full team that represented not only the region but went on to represent the country at world games.'\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that one session\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"a full team\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"not only the region\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"world games\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura, who has a sports development background, started out as a volunteer coach before joining the national office in 2019.\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3140, \"end\": 3145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999793912988887, \"rank\": 2.060912583645179e-05, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sports development background\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"a volunteer coach\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3220}, {\"ngram\": \"the national office\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was a delegate for the Special Olympics athletes who competed in Abu Dhabi 