36, \"rank\": 0.004297772384292259, \"text\": \"Portsmouth\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portsmouth_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portsmouth_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first ever athletics event\", \"from\": 4722, \"to\": 4752}, {\"ngram\": \"Katie\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4780}, {\"ngram\": \"her trainers\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4805}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4819}, {\"ngram\": \"her laces\", \"from\": 4865, \"to\": 4874}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Katie, who runs her own gardening business, recently became chair of the athlete leadership team, where she acts as a spokesperson for athletes to help get their views across during meetings with the charity's board.\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 5118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Katie\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 4907}, {\"ngram\": \"her own gardening business\", \"from\": 4918, \"to\": 4944}, {\"ngram\": \"chair\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4967}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete leadership team\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4998}, {\"ngram\": \"a spokesperson\", \"from\": 5018, \"to\": 5032}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5045}, {\"ngram\": \"their views\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5069}, {\"ngram\": \"meetings\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5092}, {\"ngram\": \"the charity's board\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was in my first year of senior school and someone recommended Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5185, \"end\": 5201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.401676227682725e-26, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first year\", \"from\": 5130, \"to\": 5143}, {\"ngram\": \"senior school\", \"from\": 5147, \"to\": 5160}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I started back in 1997 and I have been going ever since, from strength to strength,' she tells Metro.\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 5265, \"to\": 5273}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 5277, \"to\": 5285}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 5298, \"to\": 5303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My local club in Birmingham was set up in 1986 so it was a fairly new one, and we literally just walked in for a taster session and it's been \\\"eat, sleep, Special Olympics, repeat\\\" ever since.\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5324, \"end\": 5334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"score\": 0.9999999937408575, \"rank\": 6.2582845849676776e-09, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My local club\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5320}, {\"ngram\": \"a taster session\", \"from\": 5418, \"to\": 5434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It would be an incredible experience and I'd feel very proud and honoured to be representing GB when we hopefully get the 2031 games.\", \"from\": 5501, \"to\": 5635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5595, \"end\": 5597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999721148137624, \"rank\": 2.788596361007268e-05, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible experience\", \"from\": 5514, \"to\": 5538}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2031 games\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It will also highlight