": 7287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's another experience, it takes you out of your shell.\", \"from\": 7314, \"to\": 7371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another experience\", \"from\": 7320, \"to\": 7338}, {\"ngram\": \"your shell\", \"from\": 7360, \"to\": 7370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people just want to do things that keep them comfortable, but you have got to push yourself or you are not gonna achieve anything,' Bradley explains to Metro, describing the experience of stepping up from his local club to taking part in World Games.\", \"from\": 7372, \"to\": 7627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7509, \"end\": 7516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9999912786932467, \"rank\": 8.715505628580316e-06, \"text\": \"Bradley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 7372, \"to\": 7383}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 7400, \"to\": 7406}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 7498, \"to\": 7506}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 7529, \"to\": 7534}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 7547, \"to\": 7561}, {\"ngram\": \"his local club\", \"from\": 7582, \"to\": 7596}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 7607, \"to\": 7611}, {\"ngram\": \"World Games\", \"from\": 7615, \"to\": 7626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a really good experience.\", \"from\": 7629, \"to\": 7660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really good experience\", \"from\": 7635, \"to\": 7659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People have different stories, not everyone is brought up the same, people have different lifestyles.\", \"from\": 7661, \"to\": 7762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 7661, \"to\": 7667}, {\"ngram\": \"different stories\", \"from\": 7673, \"to\": 7690}, {\"ngram\": \"not everyone\", \"from\": 7692, \"to\": 7704}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7729, \"to\": 7735}, {\"ngram\": \"different lifestyles\", \"from\": 7741, \"to\": 7761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My favourite part of playing football is meeting new people - you are not just playing with the people in your club.\", \"from\": 7764, \"to\": 7881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My favourite part\", \"from\": 7765, \"to\": 7782}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 7794, \"to\": 7802}, {\"ngram\": \"new people\", \"from\": 7814, \"to\": 7824}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 7857, \"to\": 7867}, {\"ngram\": \"your club\", \"from\": 7871, \"to\": 7880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You get to meet not just people with IDs, you meet other people who did not have IDs, and being treated the same as them was really nice.'\", \"from\": 7883, \"to\": 8022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"not just people\", \"from\": 7900, \"to\": 7915}, {\"ngram\": \"IDs\", \"from\": 7921, \"to\": 7924}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 7935, \"to\": 7947}, {\"ngram\": \"IDs\", \"from\": 7965, \"to\": 7968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing his proudest achievements at the Games, Bradley adds: 'Berlin was probably the one that pushed me further than all of them and got my confidence up massively.\", \"from\": 8024, \"to\": 8193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8075, \"end\": 8082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9999912786932467, \"rank\": 8.715505628580316e-06, \"text\": \"Bradley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 8090, \"end\": 8096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"score\": 0.9720827955660364, \"rank\": 0.028718952663415002, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his proudest achievements\", \"from\": 8035, \"to\": 8060}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 8064, \"to\": 8073}, {\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 8110, \"to\": 8117}, {\"ngram\": \"my confidence\", \"from\": 8166, \"to\": 8179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When I scored my goals in Berlin, before that I was never fit enough to get the opportunity to stay on the pitch, but luckily one of our local gyms gave us free gym membership to help us prepare for the games.\", \"from\": 8195, \"to\": 8405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8222, \"end\": 8228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"score\": 0.9720827955660364, \"rank\": 0.028718952663415002, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my goals\", \"from\": 8210, \"to\": 8218}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 8272, \"to\": 8287}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 8299, \"to\": 8308}, {\"ngram\": \"our local gyms\", \"from\": 8329, \"to\": 8343}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8349, \"to\": 8351}, {\"ngram\": \"free gym membership\", \"from\": 8352, \"to\": 8371}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8380, \"to\": 8382}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 8395, \"to\": 8404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a big help.'\", \"from\": 8406, \"to\": 8427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big help\", \"from\": 8415, \"to\": 8425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigel recalls: 'Berlin was a great achievement, as a coach it was amazing, and obviously as a dad as well.\", \"from\": 8429, \"to\": 8535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8445, \"end\": 8451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"score\": 0.9720827955660364, \"rank\": 0.028718952663415002, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nigel\", \"from\": 8429, \"to\": 8434}, {\"ngram\": \"a great achievement\", \"from\": 8456, \"to\": 8475}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 8480, \"to\": 8487}, {\"ngram\": \"a dad\", \"from\": 8521, \"to\": 8526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were a few tears just seeing what Bradley's achieved.\", \"from\": 8536, \"to\": 8595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8576, \"end\": 8583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9999912786932467, \"rank\": 8.715505628580316e-06, \"text\": \"Bradley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Branning\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few tears\", \"from\": 8547, \"to\": 8558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His confidence has gone through the roof.\", \"from\": 8596, \"to\": 8637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His confidence\", \"from\": 8596, \"to\": 8610}, {\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 8628, \"to\": 8636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's about the players, and seeing what they have achieved.\", \"from\": 8639, \"to\": 8699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 8651, \"to\": 8662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of people tell then \\\"you are not good enough\\\" and \\\"you can not do this, you can not do that\\\" - they have proved them wrong.'\", \"from\": 8700, \"to\": 8830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 8700, \"to\": 8705}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 8709, \"to\": 8715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barry McFarlane, who has mild Asperger's syndrome, was interested in basketball from a young age, idolising Michael Jordan and other US stars.\", \"from\": 8832, \"to\": 8974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8832, \"end\": 8837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\", \"score\": 0.9999908088897808, \"rank\": 9.191194980646958e-06, \"text\": \"Barry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\"}, {\"begin\": 8940, \"end\": 8954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.877552287143451e-25, \"text\": \"Michael Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 8965, \"end\": 8967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9987537988393276, \"rank\": 0.001246955358678606, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mild Asperger's syndrome\", \"from\": 8857, \"to\": 8881}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 8901, \"to\": 8911}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 8917, \"to\": 8928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when he had the opportunity to join in a lunchtime club as a teenager in 2003, which brought specialist coaches into his school, he jumped at the chance.\", \"from\": 8976, \"to\": 9132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 8991, \"to\": 9006}, {\"ngram\": \"a lunchtime club\", \"from\": 9018, \"to\": 9034}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 9038, \"to\": 9048}, {\"ngram\": \"specialist coaches\", \"from\": 9072, \"to\": 9090}, {\"ngram\": \"his school\", \"from\": 9096, \"to\": 9106}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 9121, \"to\": 9131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then joined the Glasgow Eagles, his local club connected with the Special Olympics, and soon he was representing his country at games held in Glasgow in 2005.\", \"from\": 9134, \"to\": 9295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9203, \"end\": 9219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.401676227682725e-26, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 9279, \"end\": 9286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999998617568, \"rank\": 1.3412927501866498e-10, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Glasgow Eagles\", \"from\": 9149, \"to\": 9167}, {\"ngram\": \"his local club\", \"from\": 9169, \"to\": 9183}, {\"ngram\": \"his country\", \"from\": 9250, \"to\": 9261}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 9265, \"to\": 9270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was a little bit nervous about it at first, but when I went along one weekend, I knew it was the right place for me,' he tells Metro.\", \"from\": 9297, \"to\": 9433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one weekend\", \"from\": 9366, \"to\": 9377}, {\"ngram\": \"the right place\", \"from\": 9393, \"to\": 9408}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 9427, \"to\": 9432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We found out about the Games in Glasgow, and basically got training for that straight away.\", \"from\": 9435, \"to\": 9527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9468, \"end\": 9475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999998617568, \"rank\": 1.3412927501866498e-10, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9455, \"to\": 9464}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 9495, \"to\": 9503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was great to play a home game for my first time, it ranks up there as probably the best out of all the things I have achieved in my life.\", \"from\": 9529, \"to\": 9670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a home game\", \"from\": 9551, \"to\": 9562}, {\"ngram\": \"my first time\", \"from\": 9567, \"to\": 9580}, {\"ngram\": \"all the things\", \"from\": 9628, \"to\": 9642}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 9662, \"to\": 9669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a fantastic experience and it's definitely something I can look back on fondly.'\", \"from\": 9672, \"to\": 9760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fantastic experience\", \"from\": 9680, \"to\": 9702}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 9723, \"to\": 9732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While he's still an active athlete, 33-year-old Barry, a gym instructor, has also recently started to coach other players at Glasgow Eagles, which he hopes to keep doing for a long time to come.\", \"from\": 9762, \"to\": 9956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9810, \"end\": 9815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\", \"score\": 0.9999908088897808, \"rank\": 9.191194980646958e-06, \"text\": \"Barry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an active athlete\", \"from\": 9779, \"to\": 9796}, {\"ngram\": \"a gym instructor\", \"from\": 9817, \"to\": 9833}, {\"ngram\": \"other players\", \"from\": 9870, \"to\": 9883}, {\"ngram\": \"Glasgow Eagles\", \"from\": 9887, \"to\": 9901}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 9936, \"to\": 9947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing the impact the Special OIympics has had on his life, he explains.\", \"from\": 9958, \"to\": 10034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 9969, \"to\": 9979}, {\"ngram\": \"the Special OIympics\", \"from\": 9980, \"to\": 10000}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 10012, \"to\": 10020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Any time I went to any tournaments, my aim is always to enjoy myself and have fun, but at the same time, I am quite competitive and I like to win.\", \"from\": 10036, \"to\": 10183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any tournaments\", \"from\": 10056, \"to\": 10071}, {\"ngram\": \"my aim\", \"from\": 10073, \"to\": 10079}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 10115, \"to\": 10118}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 10127, \"to\": 10140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Winning golds and other medals is amazing.\", \"from\": 10185, \"to\": 10228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"golds\", \"from\": 10194, \"to\": 10199}, {\"ngram\": \"other medals\", \"from\": 10204, \"to\": 10216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Special Games is one of those experiences that will change your life forever.\", \"from\": 10230, \"to\": 10312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Special Games\", \"from\": 10231, \"to\": 10248}, {\"ngram\": \"those experiences\", \"from\": 10259, \"to\": 10276}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 10294, \"to\": 10303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you'd said to me in 2003: \\\"20 years later you will still be playing basketball and even coaching\\\" I probably would have laughed and said there was no chance.\", \"from\": 10313, \"to\": 10473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 10384, \"to\": 10394}, {\"ngram\": \"no chance\", \"from\": 10463, \"to\": 10472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But it's allowed me to pass on my experience to people who are just starting their journeys, so I have got a lot to be thankful to the Special Olympics for.\", \"from\": 10475, \"to\": 10632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10611, \"end\": 10627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.401676227682725e-26, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my experience\", \"fro